     The Mini-map (shown here in a highlighted frame) provides a quick overview of the Game zone. You can use it to see your character's current location. The Mini-map always shows the entire Game zone, regardless of how much terrain you've managed to explore.

     Different colored triangles indicate your character(s) and all those they might come into contact with.

     Green triangles represent your characters
     Yellow triangles represent neutral characters
     Red triangles represent enemies.
